{{#extend "project" }}
{{#content "title" mode="append"}} - KPCB{{/content}}
{{#content "body-class" mode="append"}} page-kpcb{{/content}}
{{#content "backgrounds" mode="append"}}
<li class="background-kpcb-hero"></li>
<li class="background-kpcb-brand"></li>
<li class="background-kpcb-print"></li>
{{/content}}
{{#content "sections" mode="prepend"}}
<li class="animated-section project-hero section-kpcb-hero" data-section-id="kpcb-hero">
    <div class="content">
        <h1 class="project-title sc-text">KPCB</h1>
        <div class="project-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/img/kpcb/kpcb-macbook.png" alt="KPCB">
            <ul class="services">
                <li class="sc-text">Brand Identity</li>
                <li class="sc-text">Print Design</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="project-summary sc-text">Kleiner Perkins Caufield Byers is one of the world's top venture capital firms. We assembled a sub-brand for their annual CEO Workshop.</p>
        <div class="blockquote-wrapper">
          <blockquote class="sbd-accent sc-text">
              <div class="quote-upper-line sbg-accent"></div>
              <div class="quote-mark sf-svg-accent">{{> "icons/quote.svg"}}</div>
              <div class="quote-lower-line sbg-accent"></div>

              The Kleiner Perkins team and guests noticed the branding much more this year and it all came together nicely.
              <cite>
                  <span class="name sc-text">Ju-Djuin Csontos</span>
                  <span class="title sc-text">Marketing Manager, KPCB</span>
                  <span class="photo"><img src="/img/kpcb/head-jd.png" alt="Ju-Djuin Csontos"></span>
              </cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-kpcb-brand" data-section-id="kpcb-brand">
    <div class="content">
          <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Setting an atmosphere for connections</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">The KPCB team expressed their interest in helping the CEOs of their portfolio companies connect in meaningful ways. The brand we created for their CEO Workshop event used a "nodes and connections" motif to demonstrate the network effect of support that KPCB was after.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <img class="project-screenshot padded" src="/img/kpcb/kpcb-logotype.svg" alt="KPCB CEO Workshop Logotype">
        </div>
    </div>
    <img class="project-screenshot full-bleed" src="/img/kpcb/grid.png" alt="KPCB Grid">
    <div class="content color-blocks">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{> color-block
              name="Black"
              hex="222222"
              class="dark"}}
            {{> color-block
              name="Light Gray"
              hex="EEEEEE"
              class="light"}}
            {{> color-block
              name="Green"
              hex="3BB780"
              class="dark with-border"}}
        </div>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="animated-section project-section section-kpcb-print" data-section-id="kpcb-print">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="h1 sc-text">Getting physical with print media</h2>
        <div class="col-8 col-centered">
            <p class="large sc-text">It was important that the program identity worked as print ephemera for the event. We extended the identity into posters, backdrops, badges, agendas, program booklets, tote bags, and signs, as well as some digital items like slide deck templates and website assets.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/kpcb/posters-together.png" alt="KPCB Posters">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-12">
          <img class="project-screenshot full-bleed" src="/img/kpcb/sign.png" alt="KPCB Grid">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="col-6">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/kpcb/photo-bags.jpg" alt="KPCB Bags">
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            <img class="project-screenshot" src="/img/kpcb/photo-panel.jpg" alrt="KPCB Backdrop">
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            <img class="project-screenshot with-above" src="/img/kpcb/photo-group.jpg" alrt="KPCB Nametags">
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
            <img class="project-screenshot with-above" src="/img/kpcb/photo-sign.jpg" alrt="KPCB Poster">
        </div>

    </div>
</li>
{{> "footer" class="solid" id="kpcb-footer" }}
{{/content}}
{{/extend}}
